\begin_layout Standard
"But we did have him, and thus the expedition is saved," Torun said with a
 careless shrug.
 "What are you being so gloomy about?"

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"What indeed," Daimen mumbled.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Anyway, now we just have to figure out how to break through this invisible
 door thing and we'll be free to loot Awan-Temti's tomb to our hearts' content,
 yes?" Torun asked.

\end_layout

