"Yes, Chassanah is right," Daimen nodded.
 "We lost too much here as it is.
 I want to hire more fighters before we try to set foot there."

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"I'd like to stay here for a while and study the entrance point for a bit,"
 Zorian said, frowning.
 "Something doesn't feel right about this."

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Fine," Daimen sighed.
 "But don't do anything before consulting me! Look, but don't touch."

