\begin_layout Standard
"That palace… it's not just a model, is it?" Zach said, sounding fascinated.
 "It's a real thing, contained inside the orb."

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Obviously," Orissa said.
 "Why would it be a ruin otherwise?"

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"So Shutur-Tarana made himself a portable palace to carry around with him at
 all times?" Zach asked rhetorically.
 "I like it."

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Yes, now imagine just how much stuff there could be stored there," Torun said
