Thus, Zach and Zorian stole a pair of fancy red robes from the Cult of the
 Dragon Below and teleported to Knyazov Dveri, where they proceeded to smash up
 store fronts, set several warehouses on fire and used alteration to call out
 Sudomir as a 'traitor to the Esoteric Order of the Celestial Dragon'.
 Zorian also used his mind magic to guide a herd of wild boars directly into
 the town square, after which he released his control over them and let them
 run amok as they pleased.

\end_layout

