The city guard tried to stop them, of course.
 They were actually pretty brutal about it, going so far as to have snipers try
 to pick them off from the rooftops, despite the fact that Zach and Zorian
 clearly avoided killing anyone themselves.
 Still, they were barely a challenge.
 Zach and Zorian simply knocked them out or otherwise incapacitated them, and
 then continued with their extended provocation.

