 middle of the battle and this was the quickest way I knew of stopping that
 from happening.
 He said he was hard to kill so I figured that he wouldn't die from blood
 loss."

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"I can't believe my previous selves thought you weren't brutal enough," Alanic
 mumbled under his breath.
 "And why is he not unconscious? I thought we agreed you'd knock him out before
 bringing him here?"

\end_layout

