\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Though he did pretend to be unconscious after we hit him with the fifth one,"
 Zorian pointed out.
 "Zach wanted to try knocking him out 'the old fashioned way' by hitting him in
 the head with a rock, but I vetoed that.
 So we just glued his mouth shut, tied his legs together, put a bag over his
 head and brought him over."

